songs.lyrics:
KUSH -

Bakcodi band log tag sath ke
Udate pese baap ke
Ye Chutiye akhir peda kyu kiye
Samjhte khud smart ye sakal se hutiye
Inke bare sochu Niklti bas ek baat

H anath kamini jaat dedu laat gand pe
Baat ko samjh pahle tu araam se
Kyu Krta bakcodiya jita tu haraam se
Naam se nhi pehchaan he
Meri kaamse
Kaam rhkhu kaam se
Darta ajanaam se

Samaan dekh mera jivan hua vatitye
Atiye ye jisme hardwork mera thik ye
Sikhiye ise  kuch to aap nhi baap
Kehna padega tujhko

Mujhko Man le
Pahle baat jan le
Bhale hi ilzaam le
Jo krna he wo thanle

Chorahe pe dekh fuke kese maal ye
Behal ye katne wale bakre hote halalye
Sawal ye janta mujhse kyu krta hu ese
Kam he pese tere jesa nhi nasib ye
Garib ye insan par dil ka he amir ye
Music dose dhuye se chalta sarir ye

Mr.HD -

Bakchodi band jede tedhi medhi baat kare
Ik nawa song teen bande mere sath khade
Aaj kal de rappers dekho ho gaye kitne shanne
Beta likhi do lines mujhse battle ki baat kare
Koi sath nahi chala apne raste fir toliyo me khade munde mujhko pukarte
Itne sare log mene kisi ko pehechana nahi fir hath mila ke bole sare merko jante he
Aaj kal call ate unknown mujhe kare request log milne ko phone
Facebook pe like kare twitter pe follow mere ghar ke pate ke sath pura naam jante he
Utra backstage mujhe mudeyan ne ghera
Thi ankh laal sabki naale kuddiyan da mela
10-12 launde mujhe security dende wo toh daru de nashe me khud ko bodyguards mante he
Meri life chale jive koi game ik pase mere mind dooje pase sam wayne
Ha
Teeje pase mere khush naale bakchodi band Mr.HD di fame huh !

MINDMAKER -

Data tana bana naana
Mujhko aakha na dikhana
Mujhsa duri tum banana
Mujha ko rap mt sikhana
Batel mujhasa na lgana
Apna gana na sunana
Apni baata mt chudana
Apni aukaat mt dikhanana
M rap likhta rhta hu mujhko na sikhana. Mujhsa duri tum bnana
Aaj dekho kasa mera gliyo pr hota kina chrcha
Jo log mera sath ghuma krta mujhpr khrcha hai
Mujhko khta mind Inki sochma hi khai hai.....


SAM WAYNE -

Haan Khai h gandi soch ne jidagi thumari khari h
Gaane ke sath ghadi bedley naya  dor laye
Naam’ mujhe bhi ni pasand mere is nave gane ka
Buckchodi suni logo ki ab time shamjhane ka

Such kuch loyal, such much original
Koi fayda nahi gadi tag or vastro pe paisa lgane ka
Thumare jhuti shano ko
Nakli thumare phechano ko
Phele bachao
Koi fayda nahi Hip Hop ko bachane ka

Hip Hop Surakshit hai
songs.title: BAKCHODI BAND
